* Littlewood, Joan (2003). &quot;Joan&#x27;s Book: The Autobiography of Joan Littlewood&quot;. London: Methuen. 
* MacColl, Ewan (1990). &quot;Journeyman: An Autobiography&quot;. London: Sidgwick &amp; Jackson. 
